chirptask.testing

Class JUnitGoogleAtd

  • java.lang.Object
    • chirptask.testing.JUnitGoogleAtd

  • public class JUnitGoogleAtd
extends java.lang.Object
    Warning: JUnitGoogleAtd takes a while to load completely There may be times where it will fail totally as it depends on your internet connection stability. Do take the factor of how slow/unstable the internet may be if the JUnit Test failed. The sleep(milliseconds) were added in their positions because there is no easy way to tell when the Google requests are completed. This is because they are running in the background threads. Note that we MUST finish the initial StorageHandler.initCloudStorage() before starting the test.
